{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_04_01",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 1話 アイドルと学生の狭間で",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん。お疲れ様です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san. Good work!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.2333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、奥山さん。……最近あんまり元気がない\n気がするんだけど、大丈夫か？　疲れてない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ Okuyama-san… I feel like you haven't been energetic\nlately. Are you okay? Not tired?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3129538854,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　そ、そんなことないですよ！？\n私はいつも元気一杯です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? Th-That's not true at all!\nI'm always full of energy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……本当に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Really?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよ、元気元気……\nって、言いたいところなんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ really‚ full of energy…\nWell‚ that's what I want to say‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "さっき、瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんにも\n心配されたんですよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but earlier‚ Rui-chan and Yu-chan\nwere also worried about me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "何か悩みがあるなら相談してほしい\n俺は奥山さんのマネージャーなんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you have any worries‚ I want you to talk to me.\nI'm Okuyama-san's manager‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "そう言われると……ちょっと甘えたくなっちゃいますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you say that… makes me want to lean in a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとだけ、お時間いただいていいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can I have a little bit of your time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "最近、トリエルの活動だけじゃなくて\n私個人のお仕事も増えてきましたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately‚ not just TRINITYAiLE's activities‚\nmy personal work has been increasing‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、奥山さん単独の人気も高まってきてると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I think Okuyama-san's popularity as an individual is also rising.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "忙しくなること自体はいいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being busy itself is fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事は楽しいし、勉強になるし……\n何より、みなさんに必要とされることが嬉しいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Works are fun and I learn a lot.\nBut most importantly‚ it makes me happy to be needed by everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "でも……この間学校の授業で\n中学校の思い出を作文で振り返る時間があったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… the other day‚ during a school class‚\nwe had time to reflect on our memories from middle school through an essay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "最近は東京にいる時間が少しずつ長くなっていて\n学校行事にもあんまり参加出来ていなかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately‚ my time in Tokyo has been gradually increasing‚\nso I couldn't participate in many school events.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "友達と比べて、あんまり書けることがなくて……えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Compared to my friends‚ I didn't have much to write about… hehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "それなら友達とのことを書けば……と思ったんですけど\n遊びに誘ってもらっても行けないことが多くて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought maybe I could write about my friends…\nbut there were many times I couldn't go even when they invited me to hang out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……寂しい思いをさせてしまってすまない\nちょっと仕事をセーブしようか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… I'm sorry for making you feel lonely.\nShould we slow down on work a bit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ、大丈夫ですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh no‚ it's okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "というか、{user}さんの場合……\n私に気を遣って、相談なしに仕事を断っちゃいそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In fact‚ in your case‚ {user}-san…\nIf I let you worry about me‚ you might start refusing work without asking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの絶対ダメですからね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's absolutely not allowed‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはしないよ。ちゃんと相談するから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won't do that. I'll make sure to ask you properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "それならいいんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ it's fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "でも……沢山お仕事はしたいなって思ってても\nいろいろ考えちゃうんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… even though I want to do a lot of work‚\nI end up overthinking things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_04_01-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "子役をやってた時も同じようなことがあったので\nもっと学校生活を楽しんでおけば良かったのかなーとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had similar thoughts when I was a child actor too‚\nlike if I should have enjoyed my school life more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
